    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将削减预算中的主要全球经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/australia-to-cut-key-global-economy-growth-forecasts-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，澳大利亚将在下个月发布预算时下调包括主要贸易伙伴中国在内的大多数主要经济体的增长前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/australia-to-cut-key-global-economy-growth-forecasts-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织面临反对新兴市场债务重做蓝图的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界金融领导人正在推动彻底改革主权债务重组体系，该体系使贫穷国家被排除在资本市场之外，因为中国作为关键参与者的出现颠覆了传统谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅希望重新夺回主动权，泽伦斯基欢呼美国的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局对美国众议院批准超过 600 亿美元的援助感到欢欣鼓舞，不过焦点正在转移到援助能够以多快的速度到达前线，以及该计划将如何改变基辅在对抗俄罗斯入侵的斗争中的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 11:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉利用周末降低汽车和 FSD 软件价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/tesla-cuts-china-us-prices-after-sales-slow-inventories-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销量下滑和库存过剩，特斯拉公司上周末下调了其在中国、欧洲和美国的车型价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/tesla-cuts-china-us-prices-after-sales-slow-inventories-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 01:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国是黄金破纪录上涨的前沿和中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/china-is-front-and-center-of-gold-s-record-breaking-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年金价升至每盎司 2,400 美元以上的历史高位，吸引了全球市场。中国是全球最大的贵金属生产国和消费国，处于这一非凡崛起的前沿和中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/china-is-front-and-center-of-gold-s-record-breaking-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡干细胞库毁掉数千个样本后家长愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/cordlife-scandal-fury-as-thousands-of-stem-cell-samples-destroyed-in-singapore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲脐带血库的一家主要运营商因处理不当对孩子们的样本造成了不可挽回的损害，新加坡数千名家长对此感到愤怒，其中一些家长正在寻求法律诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/cordlife-scandal-fury-as-thousands-of-stem-cell-samples-destroyed-in-singapore</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国新股领军企业面临越来越多的贸易调查浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trade-tensions-threaten-the-rise-of-china-s-stock-champions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最有前途的行业正面临西方政府日益增长的贸易限制威胁，这使得有潜力推动中国市场增长的股票前景变得模糊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trade-tensions-threaten-the-rise-of-china-s-stock-champions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储首选通胀指标将支持降息耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员即将得到进一步确认，证明对抗通胀的进展已陷入停滞，这支持了基调的转变，将利率维持在比先前预期更长的时间内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于销售放缓、库存增加，特斯拉在美国降价 2,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tesla-cuts-prices-by-2-000-as-sales-slow-inventories-swell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于第一季度销量令人失望导致库存膨胀，特斯拉公司将其最畅销的 Model Y、Model S 和 X 的价格下调了 2,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tesla-cuts-prices-by-2-000-as-sales-slow-inventories-swell</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
